title: Veeam Scale-Out Repositories
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam Scale-Out Backup Repositories (SOBR) via the REST API.

 It reports:
 - Number of performance extents and their health status
 - Extent status (Normal, Sealed, Maintenance, Evacuate, etc.)
 - Capacity tier status (enabled/disabled, offload status)
 - Archive tier status
 - Placement policy type

 The check returns:
 - OK: All extents are healthy
 - WARN: Extents in Maintenance, Evacuate, or ResyncRequired state
 - WARN: No performance extents configured

discovery:
 One service is created for each scale-out backup repository.

item:
 The scale-out repository name
